{"tid":1242910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李家超：速龍小隊工作制服　無位置展示警員編號","createTime":"2019-06-19T08:53:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T09:25:40.000Z","uid":90318,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ed7694008bff651ca72f3fa0fe28af4667344862","tid":1242910,"uid":90318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:53:01.000Z","msg":"警方在 612 衝突（上周三）中出動俗稱「速龍小隊」的特別戰術小隊，清場手法極受爭議，小隊亦被質疑制服上未有警員編號，保安局局長李家超今在立法會大會指出，從警方得到資料，「速龍小隊」特別保護工作服沒有位置展示警員編號，他稱警方明白公眾關注會作檢視。<br />\n<br />\n立法會大會今天自 6.12 警民衝突後首次召開會議，民主派議員提出緊急質詢追究警方濫權。公民黨譚文豪在緊急質詢中指出，便衣警在行使警權時，是否需要出示委任證，當有市民要求出示委任證，便衣警有沒有權拒絕委任證，以及「速龍小隊」制服是否需要展示警員編號等。<br />\n<br />\n李家超指出，從警方得到資料，「<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">特別戰術小隊的特別保護工作服，是根據行動、戰術需要設計，工作服的設計沒有位置展示警員的編號</span></span>。同時在行動中會盡可能展示編號，警方明白公眾的關注，會在這方面作出檢視。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/6-12-%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98-%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85-%E9%80%9F%E9%BE%8D%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E6%9C%8D-%E7%84%A1%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%B7%A8%E8%99%9F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F6-12-%25E4%25BD%2594%25E9%25A0%2598-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B6%2585-%25E9%2580%259F%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%259C%258D-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BD%258D%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E5%25B1%2595%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25B7%25A8%25E8%2599%259F%2F&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dZq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=f3cc840f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F6-12-%25E4%25BD%2594%25E9%25A0%2598-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B6%2585-%25E9%2580%259F%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%259C%258D-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BD%258D%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E5%25B1%2595%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25B7%25A8%25E8%2599%259F%2F&h=ccd73287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/6-12-%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98-%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85-%E9%80%9F%E9%BE%8D%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E6%9C%8D-%E7%84%A1%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%B7%A8%E8%99%9F/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377a3e3204da54683a06d3182cc731c2c2080860","tid":1242910,"uid":41389,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:53:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔 好 再 打 飛 機 星 期 五 出 黎 野 餐</span></span>"},{"pid":"67180074bc7e2fa2c9e8a4cbf872e9f228366729","tid":1242910,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:54:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c6e0bf337e024f50690a5e3c665059233182e2e","tid":1242910,"uid":129013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:14:01.000Z","msg":"佢知唔知自己講緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7315bd41aa641c2041ee084812103cb25933e0","tid":1242910,"uid":9104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:16:39.000Z","msg":"好似球衣咁連名印係背脊正中央 印埋前面"},{"pid":"30b1477ded4569d68e205c8a588cdf68f2c1e974","tid":1242910,"uid":36845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:18:20.000Z","msg":"咁咪撚俾畜龍著<br />\n炒撚左設計條友，間接令到警員違反《警察通例》<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c64c7540483d36f7457bf63e5be3fd943529887","tid":1242910,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"大支野到"},{"pid":"d282e847006277f513e9c24c406567a74dbce06c","tid":12429